trans-unit.source: Manages the definition of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_IEnumConnections" name="IEnumConnections" href=""></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: Administrerer definisjonen av den <xref uid="langword_csharp_IEnumConnections" name="IEnumConnections" href=""> </xref> grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Functions and objects in the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6> namespace are provided for use by the tools for upgrading from Visual Basic 6.0 to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Funksjoner og objekter i den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>navneområde er angitt for bruk av verktøyene for oppgradering fra Visual Basic 6.0 til [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>

trans-unit.source: In most cases, these functions and objects duplicate functionality that you can find in other namespaces in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: I de fleste tilfeller disse funksjonene og objekter duplisert funksjonaliteten som du finner andre navneområder i den [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: They are necessary only when the Visual Basic 6.0 code model differs significantly from the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementation.
trans-unit.target: De er nødvendige bare når Visual Basic 6.0 kode modellen er forskjellig betydelig fra den [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementeringen.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new enumerator that contains the same enumeration state as the current one.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny opplisting som inneholder samme opplisting tilstand som det gjeldende.

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains a reference to the newly created enumerator.
trans-unit.target: Låse denne metoden, inneholder en referanse til den nyopprettede opplistingen.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a specified number of items in the enumeration sequence.
trans-unit.target: Henter et angitt antall elementer i opplistingen sekvensen.

trans-unit.source: The number of <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.CONNECTDATA"></xref> structures to return in `cd`.
trans-unit.target: Antall <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.CONNECTDATA"> </xref> strukturer til å returnere i `cd`.

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains a reference to the enumerated connections.
trans-unit.target: Låse denne metoden, inneholder en referanse til nummererte tilkoblinger.

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains a reference to the actual number of connections enumerated in `cd`.
trans-unit.target: Låse denne metoden, inneholder en referanse til faktisk antall tilkoblinger som er listet opp i `cd`.

trans-unit.source: Resets the enumeration sequence to the start.
Skips a specified number of items in the enumeration sequence.
trans-unit.target: Hopper over et angitt antall elementer i opplistingen sekvensen.

trans-unit.source: The number of elements to skip in the enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Antallet elementer å hoppe over i opplistingen.
